Dialogue: 0.0:02:03.54.0:02:05.46.Default..0.0.0..Najid. cut the horses loose!
Dialogue: 0.0:02:57.38.0:02:59.05.Default..0.0.0..We have to turn back.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:59.17.0:03:01.27.Default..0.0.0..We have been riding for six months.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:01.43.0:03:03.27.Default..0.0.0..And we've lost 20 men.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:03.43.0:03:04.73.Default..0.0.0..But we survived.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:04.85.0:03:06.69.Default..0.0.0..Yes. By chance.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:06.81.0:03:10.11.Default..0.0.0..Any one of us could have met that same fate.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:10.27.0:03:12.27.Default..0.0.0..We were the strongest.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:12.60.0:03:14.28.Default..0.0.0..Remember why you're here.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:14.44.0:03:18.19.Default..0.0.0..In the West. we would be enemies.\Nand I would have to kill you.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:18.61.0:03:20.11.Default..0.0.0..At least here. we have a common goal.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:20.28.0:03:21.40.Default..0.0.0..Oh. yes.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:21.49.0:03:23.08.Default..0.0.0..This black powder.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:23.66.0:03:25.58.Default..0.0.0..It turns air into fire.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:26.12.0:03:28.37.Default..0.0.0..And kills a dozen men at one time.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:28.45.0:03:30.38.Default..0.0.0..It is the weapon of our dreams.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:30.46.0:03:31.96.Default..0.0.0..And what if it's just a myth?
Dialogue: 0.0:03:32.62.0:03:34.97.Default..0.0.0..Men have sent word that it's real.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:35.09.0:03:36.26.Default..0.0.0..And those men are dead.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:36.34.0:03:37.71.Default..0.0.0..And we are next.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:38.30.0:03:39.67.Default..0.0.0..We have no maps.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:39.80.0:03:41.14.Default..0.0.0..no medicine
Dialogue: 0.0:03:41.26.0:03:42.38.Default..0.0.0..and no food.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:42.97.0:03:44.14.Default..0.0.0..No one is going back.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:45.05.0:03:48.18.Default..0.0.0..We take inventory of what we have left
Dialogue: 0.0:03:48.35.0:03:50.48.Default..0.0.0..and finish what we started.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:50.56.0:03:52.65.Default..0.0.0..There's not much here.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:53.31.0:03:54.69.Default..0.0.0..The moon is strong.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:54.81.0:03:56.82.Default..0.0.0..When the horses are fresh. we move.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:56.90.0:03:58.78.Default..0.0.0..- To where?\N North.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:59.36.0:04:02.41.Default..0.0.0..If they keep after us.\Nwe'll kill them in the mountains.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:02.53.0:04:03.91.Default..0.0.0..The magnet.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:06.16.0:04:07.71.Default..0.0.0..Too heavy.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:07.83.0:04:08.95.Default..0.0.0..Useless.\N- I'll have it.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:11.00.0:04:12.12.Default..0.0.0..It's all yours.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:17.09.0:04:20.97.Default..0.0.0..Amigo. only you would carry\Na stupid magnet through the desert.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:21.05.0:04:22.64.Default..0.0.0..I can use it to make a compass.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:25.34.0:04:27.52.Default..0.0.0..Rizzetti won't make it.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:28.26.0:04:30.52.Default..0.0.0..The wound is festering.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:30.68.0:04:32.10.Default..0.0.0..We'll be dragging a corpse.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:32.18.0:04:34.28.Default..0.0.0..I heard that.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:35.10.0:04:37.36.Default..0.0.0..He's earned the right to die where he wants.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:39.36.0:04:40.90.Default..0.0.0..I've been left for dead twice.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:41.53.0:04:43.15.Default..0.0.0..- It was bad luck.\N- For who?
Dialogue: 0.0:04:43.24.0:04:44.95.Default..0.0.0..- The people who left me.\N
Dialogue: 0.0:04:45.53.0:04:46.95.Default..0.0.0..Maybe Rizzetti's right.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:10.81.0:05:12.10.Default..0.0.0..Where are they?
Dialogue: 0.0:05:24.61.0:05:25.86.Default..0.0.0..Hill tribes?
Dialogue: 0.0:05:26.57.0:05:27.87.Default..0.0.0..It's no man.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:29.45.0:05:30.87.Default..0.0.0..Then what is it?
Dialogue: 0.0:05:31.41.0:05:34.71.Default..0.0.0..Whatever it is. it's hunting.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:45.80.0:05:47.43.Default..0.0.0..- What was that?\N- I don't know.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:48.18.0:05:49.60.Default..0.0.0..I took its hand.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:49.72.0:05:52.10.Default..0.0.0..We need to move.\N Agreed.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:52.22.0:05:53.47.Default..0.0.0..I'll take the hand with us.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:53.60.0:05:54.85.Default..0.0.0..What the hell for?
Dialogue: 0.0:05:55.77.0:05:58.15.Default..0.0.0..So someone can tell me what I just killed.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:14.62.0:06:16.96.Default..0.0.0..Persistent bastards. aren't they?
Dialogue: 0.0:06:17.66.0:06:20.63.Default..0.0.0..We'll take the rise. make a stand there.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:21.29.0:06:24.47.Default..0.0.0..What a long shitting way to go to die.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:11.64.0:07:13.14.Default..0.0.0..Mother of God.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:49.97.0:07:52.81.Default..0.0.0..I have no need to go down fighting.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:53.05.0:07:54.39.Default..0.0.0..Agreed.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:55.43.0:07:58.40.Default..0.0.0..I say we take our chances\Nwith the gents in front of us.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:58.56.0:08:01.06.Default..0.0.0..I haven't surrendered in a while. eh?
Dialogue: 0.0:08:03.19.0:08:05.11.Default..0.0.0..It'll come back to you.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:12.28.0:08:14.70.Default..0.0.0..Follow my lead. we'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:15.37.0:08:16.87.Default..0.0.0..Of course. my friend.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:17.03.0:08:18.71.Default..0.0.0..Where you go. I follow.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:18.79.0:08:20.71.Default..0.0.0..You're doing such a great job already.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:02.41.0:09:04.13.Default..0.0.0..They know what it is.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:04.21.0:09:05.63.Default..0.0.0..And they don't look happy to see it.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:06.21.0:09:08.46.Default..0.0.0..All the more reason\Nto get the hell out of here.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:08.59.0:09:10.51.Default..0.0.0..Our weapons are on that table.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:12.30.0:09:14.14.Default..0.0.0..Have you lost your mind?
Dialogue: 0.0:09:14.22.0:09:16.64.Default..0.0.0..I can take out the guards\Non the perimeter with my bow.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:16.80.0:09:18.43.Default..0.0.0..You cut the legs out from under the officers.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:18.60.0:09:21.14.Default..0.0.0..I must confess. this is not my favorite plan.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:21.22.0:09:23.57.Default..0.0.0..LIN: Where was this found?
Dialogue: 0.0:09:26.14.0:09:27.82.Default..0.0.0..You speak English.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:28.27.0:09:29.49.Default..0.0.0..Fantastic.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:32.78.0:09:34.49.Default..0.0.0..Where was this found?
Dialogue: 0.0:09:35.28.0:09:37.00.Default..0.0.0..It wasn't found.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:37.57.0:09:38.82.Default..0.0.0..It was taken.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:38.91.0:09:41.21.Default..0.0.0..That thing killed three men\Nbefore we took it down.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:41.41.0:09:42.41.Default..0.0.0..Where?
Dialogue: 0.0:09:43.37.0:09:44.84.Default..0.0.0..Two days' ride.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:45.00.0:09:47.55.Default..0.0.0..North. in the mountains.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:04.35.0:10:06.57.Default..0.0.0..Two of you. you did this?
Dialogue: 0.0:10:06.73.0:10:08.57.Default..0.0.0..Well...
Dialogue: 0.0:10:08.65.0:10:09.90.Default..0.0.0..I killed it.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:10.02.0:10:11.40.Default..0.0.0..Alone?
Dialogue: 0.0:10:20.62.0:10:22.33.Default..0.0.0..Tell me how.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:23.16.0:10:24.71.Default..0.0.0..A swing of the sword.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:24.83.0:10:26.88.Default..0.0.0..The hand. it came away clean.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:27.58.0:10:29.92.Default..0.0.0..The beast fell back into a chasm.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:30.50.0:10:32.09.Default..0.0.0..Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0.0:10:32.21.0:10:33.93.Default..0.0.0..We came to trade.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:34.05.0:10:36.01.Default..0.0.0..We were ambushed.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:50.10.0:10:51.23.Default..0.0.0..You are soldiers.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:02.03.0:11:03.03.Default..0.0.0..Mmm.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:22.86.0:12:24.61.Default..0.0.0..Are you killing us. sister?
Dialogue: 0.0:12:24.74.0:12:26.83.Default..0.0.0..Two lost travelers?
Dialogue: 0.0:12:31.66.0:12:33.13.Default..0.0.0..I think she'd like that.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:34.83.0:12:38.43.Default..0.0.0..If it is death. my dear.\Nwe need time to pray.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:39.13.0:12:40.22.Default..0.0.0..I'm trying here.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:42.01.0:12:44.81.Default..0.0.0..Sister. I know a siege when I see one.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:45.47.0:12:47.97.Default..0.0.0..What comes at you so hard\Nyou need a wall like this?
Dialogue: 0.0:12:48.10.0:12:49.89.Default..0.0.0..What the hell did we kill out there?
Dialogue: 0.0:12:50.01.0:12:51.52.Default..0.0.0..Tao Tei.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:52.18.0:12:54.53.Default..0.0.0..You killed a Tao Tei scout.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:54.60.0:12:55.98.Default..0.0.0..You killed it alone.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:56.60.0:12:57.82.Default..0.0.0..You're correct.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:57.90.0:12:59.32.Default..0.0.0..We are under siege.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:00.02.0:13:02.70.Default..0.0.0..But we did not expect the attack\Nfor another nine days.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:02.86.0:13:05.03.Default..0.0.0..Attack? Tao Tei.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:05.66.0:13:07.41.Default..0.0.0..What the hell is a Tao Tei?
Dialogue: 0.0:13:07.53.0:13:09.79.Default..0.0.0..Many things about your story have importance.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:10.37.0:13:11.75.Default..0.0.0..You are not to die today.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:56.58.0:15:58.83.Default..0.0.0..The black are the foot soldiers.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:59.12.0:16:00.12.Default..0.0.0..And the red?
Dialogue: 0.0:16:00.29.0:16:01.41.Default..0.0.0..Those are the archers.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:18.18.0:16:19.90.Default..0.0.0..And the blue?
Dialogue: 0.0:16:20.06.0:16:21.48.Default..0.0.0..They're all women.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:21.64.0:16:22.81.Default..0.0.0..What the hell do they do?
Dialogue: 0.0:16:37.28.0:16:39.04.Default..0.0.0..Look at this army.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:40.12.0:16:41.87.Default..0.0.0..Have you ever seen anything like this?
Dialogue: 0.0:16:41.95.0:16:43.58.Default..0.0.0..Incredible.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:03.56.0:17:05.36.Default..0.0.0..They look nervous.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:06.44.0:17:09.24.Default..0.0.0..It's a big wall to be so nervous.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:27.54.0:17:29.17.Default..0.0.0..Do you hear it?
Dialogue: 0.0:20:02.15.0:20:04.41.Default..0.0.0..William. over there.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:06.08.0:20:07.92.Default..0.0.0..Why isn't he tied up?
Dialogue: 0.0:20:09.62.0:20:10.87.Default..0.0.0..There's our escape.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:41.55.0:21:42.97.Default..0.0.0..We need to move!
Dialogue: 0.0:21:43.05.0:21:44.67.Default..0.0.0..We need to move or we die!
Dialogue: 0.0:22:02.69.0:22:03.69.Default..0.0.0..Go. go!
Dialogue: 0.0:22:05.40.0:22:06.53.Default..0.0.0..Go and fight!
Dialogue: 0.0:22:12.91.0:22:14.75.Default..0.0.0..Cut me loose!
Dialogue: 0.0:22:18.54.0:22:19.54.Default..0.0.0..Fight or run?
Dialogue: 0.0:22:19.63.0:22:20.63.Default..0.0.0..Run where?
Dialogue: 0.0:22:26.05.0:22:28.22.Default..0.0.0..Aim for the eyes!
Dialogue: 0.0:23:07.63.0:23:08.63.Default..0.0.0..William!
Dialogue: 0.0:23:35.28.0:23:37.08.Default..0.0.0..Hey! Bitch!
Dialogue: 0.0:23:53.01.0:23:54.31.Default..0.0.0..William.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:54.43.0:23:55.81.Default..0.0.0..I need a shot.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:43.39.0:24:45.69.Default..0.0.0..What god made those things?
Dialogue: 0.0:24:46.69.0:24:48.53.Default..0.0.0..None that we know.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:06.50.0:25:08.22.Default..0.0.0..Think they'll hang us now?
Dialogue: 0.0:25:08.38.0:25:10.43.Default..0.0.0..I could use the rest.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:38.03.0:25:39.75.Default..0.0.0..You've earned General Shao's praise.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:39.87.0:25:41.41.Default..0.0.0..Will they come back?
Dialogue: 0.0:25:41.54.0:25:42.54.Default..0.0.0..Yes.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:43.12.0:25:45.75.Default..0.0.0..All we can do is prepare.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:20.26.0:27:21.93.Default..0.0.0..Who are you?
Dialogue: 0.0:27:27.52.0:27:29.02.Default..0.0.0..Easy.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:31.94.0:27:33.91.Default..0.0.0..I'm Ballard. Hmm?
Dialogue: 0.0:27:35.07.0:27:36.24.Default..0.0.0..William.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:37.07.0:27:38.49.Default..0.0.0..This is Tovar.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:39.57.0:27:41.41.Default..0.0.0..What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0.0:27:42.49.0:27:44.54.Default..0.0.0..We came looking for black powder.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:44.62.0:27:46.87.Default..0.0.0..I bet you did.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:46.95.0:27:49.71.Default..0.0.0..I came with mercenaries for the same thing.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:49.79.0:27:51.42.Default..0.0.0..Twenty-five years ago.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:52.21.0:27:53.38.Default..0.0.0..And did you find it?
Dialogue: 0.0:27:53.54.0:27:56.67.Default..0.0.0..Finding it and leaving with it alive\Nare two different things.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:00.09.0:28:03.69.Default..0.0.0..You saved the west turret.\NThat was extremely diplomatic.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:03.76.0:28:05.73.Default..0.0.0..We weren't being diplomatic.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:05.80.0:28:07.52.Default..0.0.0..We were trying to stay alive.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:10.14.0:28:12.77.Default..0.0.0..- You smell like animals.\N- Thank you.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:18.32.0:28:19.66.Default..0.0.0..Clean up
Dialogue: 0.0:28:20.53.0:28:22.33.Default..0.0.0..and they'll feed you.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:24.45.0:28:26.54.Default..0.0.0..He knows where the powder is.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:28.12.0:28:29.79.Default..0.0.0..Then why is he still here?
Dialogue: 0.0:28:30.58.0:28:32.08.Default..0.0.0..He needs help getting out?
Dialogue: 0.0:28:32.71.0:28:33.71.Default..0.0.0..Right.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:34.71.0:28:36.43.Default..0.0.0..We play our part.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:36.54.0:28:39.51.Default..0.0.0..take the powder and go home.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:40.84.0:28:42.39.Default..0.0.0..I didn't sign up for this.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:42.51.0:28:43.55.Default..0.0.0..Which part?
Dialogue: 0.0:28:44.76.0:28:47.48.Default..0.0.0..Well. all of it. But mostly the monsters.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:48.47.0:28:49.77.Default..0.0.0..There's a lot of them.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:53.14.0:28:55.19.Default..0.0.0..We really do smell.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:27.47.0:29:30.39.Default..0.0.0..General Shao welcomes you as honored guests
Dialogue: 0.0:29:30.51.0:29:34.69.Default..0.0.0..of the Nameless Order and thanks you\Nfor your skill and courage.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:37.10.0:29:40.36.Default..0.0.0..We are honored to be honored.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:42.65.0:29:44.15.Default..0.0.0..Is that the best you've got?
Dialogue: 0.0:30:01.30.0:30:04.89.Default..0.0.0..Commander Chen\Nthinks your bow is not worthy of your skill.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:05.47.0:30:07.84.Default..0.0.0..Tell him there's no better weapon here.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:25.78.0:30:27.58.Default..0.0.0..They wish to see you shoot.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:28.07.0:30:29.07.Default..0.0.0..In here?
Dialogue: 0.0:30:33.24.0:30:34.34.Default..0.0.0..What was that?
Dialogue: 0.0:30:34.45.0:30:35.67.Default..0.0.0..He thinks you have fear.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:36.83.0:30:38.50.Default..0.0.0..Too many people.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:41.79.0:30:43.09.Default..0.0.0..Get one of the cups.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:43.25.0:30:44.51.Default..0.0.0..- Now?\N- Get one of the cups.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:44.59.0:30:45.59.Default..0.0.0..I want to eat.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:53.64.0:30:54.64.Default..0.0.0..You remember how to do this?
Dialogue: 0.0:30:54.77.0:30:56.98.Default..0.0.0..- Last time didn't go so good.\N- We were drunk.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:57.77.0:30:58.77.Default..0.0.0..How high?
Dialogue: 0.0:30:58.94.0:31:01.78.Default..0.0.0..Ten yards. Six hands to the right.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:01.86.0:31:03.03.Default..0.0.0..Turn around.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:03.19.0:31:04.44.Default..0.0.0..No. I'll do it this way.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:05.03.0:31:06.49.Default..0.0.0..- On my count.\N- Amigo...
Dialogue: 0.0:31:06.65.0:31:08.15.Default..0.0.0..One.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:08.28.0:31:09.28.Default..0.0.0..Two.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:10.45.0:31:11.62.Default..0.0.0..Three.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:13.08.0:31:14.70.Default..0.0.0..Pull.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:49.99.0:31:51.66.Default..0.0.0..Good luck with that.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:51.82.0:31:53.50.Default..0.0.0..I want food.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:53.57.0:31:55.04.Default..0.0.0..Who taught you English?
Dialogue: 0.0:31:55.62.0:31:56.66.Default..0.0.0..Sir Ballard.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:58.37.0:32:00.12.Default..0.0.0..English and Latin.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:01.08.0:32:03.33.Default..0.0.0..Heard he's been here for 25 years.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:03.42.0:32:05.47.Default..0.0.0..You won't let him leave.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:05.84.0:32:07.30.Default..0.0.0..He must stay here.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:08.00.0:32:09.13.Default..0.0.0..What about us?
Dialogue: 0.0:32:12.22.0:32:13.76.Default..0.0.0..Pace yourself.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:13.84.0:32:15.31.Default..0.0.0..The meals are regular here.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:15.93.0:32:17.85.Default..0.0.0..I hope not to stay that long.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:18.01.0:32:22.32.Default..0.0.0..I like your thinking. but I suggest\Nyou keep your plans private.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:22.39.0:32:26.32.Default..0.0.0..You aren't the first Westerners\Nto come here looking for black powder.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:27.19.0:32:30.66.Default..0.0.0..We'll discuss it tonight. Bring your partner.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:30.78.0:32:32.25.Default..0.0.0..How long have you been here?
Dialogue: 0.0:32:32.36.0:32:33.41.Default..0.0.0..Always.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:33.53.0:32:36.63.Default..0.0.0..I was not five years old when I came here.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:36.78.0:32:38.88.Default..0.0.0..I have no other family.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:39.04.0:32:40.71.Default..0.0.0..We're the same.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:40.79.0:32:43.76.Default..0.0.0..I was given to an army before I can remember.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:43.83.0:32:45.13.Default..0.0.0..As a soldier?
Dialogue: 0.0:32:45.21.0:32:48.05.Default..0.0.0..Worse. As a gleaner.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:48.13.0:32:51.01.Default..0.0.0..Packs of children.\Nwe'd clean the battlefields.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:51.09.0:32:53.18.Default..0.0.0..After. when the fighting's over.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:53.26.0:32:56.56.Default..0.0.0..I became a page. a pikeman's boy...
Dialogue: 0.0:32:56.68.0:32:58.60.Default..0.0.0..For your country?
Dialogue: 0.0:32:58.72.0:33:01.40.Default..0.0.0..No. I fought for food.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:02.35.0:33:03.94.Default..0.0.0..You fight to eat.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:04.60.0:33:06.53.Default..0.0.0..You live long enough. you fight for money.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:07.44.0:33:09.82.Default..0.0.0..How many flags do you fight for?
Dialogue: 0.0:33:11.19.0:33:12.87.Default..0.0.0..I don't know.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:14.78.0:33:17.28.Default..0.0.0..I fought for Harold against the Danes.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:17.41.0:33:20.75.Default..0.0.0..I saved a Duke's life.\NI fought for him until he died.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:21.29.0:33:23.91.Default..0.0.0..Fought for Spain against the Franks.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:24.25.0:33:25.92.Default..0.0.0..Fought for the Franks against Boulogne.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:26.04.0:33:27.79.Default..0.0.0..I fought for the Pope.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:29.84.0:33:31.76.Default..0.0.0..Many flags.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:35.05.0:33:37.10.Default..0.0.0..We are not the same.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:43.56.0:33:46.78.Default..0.0.0..Meet me on the Wall.\NI have something to show you.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:49.94.0:33:52.61.Default..0.0.0..He should be careful with her.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:52.69.0:33:54.29.Default..0.0.0..She's very powerful here.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:54.40.0:33:56.83.Default..0.0.0..Then it is a fair contest.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:06.33.0:34:07.46.Default..0.0.0..Come.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:19.89.0:34:21.89.Default..0.0.0..- Hmm.\N- You wish to try?
Dialogue: 0.0:34:31.15.0:34:33.82.Default..0.0.0..She says men have so much to teach us.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:40.49.0:34:42.16.Default..0.0.0..I don't think that's what she said.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:42.70.0:34:44.29.Default..0.0.0..You know what I think?
Dialogue: 0.0:34:45.25.0:34:46.37.Default..0.0.0..I think you're afraid.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:48.96.0:34:50.83.Default..0.0.0..You said that this morning.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:51.08.0:34:52.09.Default..0.0.0..And yet.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:53.84.0:34:55.68.Default..0.0.0..- here I am.\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:56.55.0:34:57.97.Default..0.0.0..Here you are.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:13.77.0:35:16.65.Default..0.0.0..Will you jump? Or not?
Dialogue: 0.0:35:19.61.0:35:21.54.Default..0.0.0..These men know what they're doing?
Dialogue: 0.0:35:21.66.0:35:22.70.Default..0.0.0..Wrong question.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:26.75.0:35:29.67.Default..0.0.0..Whether or not the cable is attached.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:30.37.0:35:32.80.Default..0.0.0..- that is the question.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:34.75.0:35:36.01.Default..0.0.0..And the answer?
Dialogue: 0.0:35:39.01.0:35:40.38.Default..0.0.0..Xin ren.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:41.76.0:35:45.14.Default..0.0.0..\NXin ren means trust. To have faith.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:46.22.0:35:48.77.Default..0.0.0..Here. in this army.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:49.43.0:35:52.06.Default..0.0.0..we fight for more than food or money.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:52.44.0:35:54.61.Default..0.0.0..We give our lives to something more.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:56.52.0:35:58.90.Default..0.0.0..Xin ren is our flag.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:59.44.0:36:01.29.Default..0.0.0..Trust in each other.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:01.86.0:36:05.41.Default..0.0.0..In all ways. at all times.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:19.59.0:36:22.18.Default..0.0.0..Well. that's all well and good.\Nbut I'm not jumping.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:22.26.0:36:25.60.Default..0.0.0..I'm alive today because I trust no one.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:26.76.0:36:28.94.Default..0.0.0..A man must learn to trust
Dialogue: 0.0:36:29.10.0:36:31.48.Default..0.0.0..before he can be trusted.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:31.60.0:36:33.57.Default..0.0.0..Then you were right.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:34.27.0:36:36.07.Default..0.0.0..We're not the same.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:54.46.0:36:59.26.Default..0.0.0..A few pilfered grains from Strategist\NWang's supply of black powder.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:00.63.0:37:04.81.Default..0.0.0..He's mastered the transmutation\Nof these elements.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:04.97.0:37:06.27.Default..0.0.0..People speak of a weapon.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:06.43.0:37:08.15.Default..0.0.0..There are many weapons here.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:08.30.0:37:09.60.Default..0.0.0..Why have we not seen them?
Dialogue: 0.0:37:09.68.0:37:12.90.Default..0.0.0..There are many things you have not seen.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:12.98.0:37:16.36.Default..0.0.0..And many things you should pray\Nwill not be needed
Dialogue: 0.0:37:16.52.0:37:18.90.Default..0.0.0..before the siege is through.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:21.36.0:37:23.99.Default..0.0.0..The Tao Tei will return.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:24.45.0:37:26.54.Default..0.0.0..When the drums call to battle.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:27.49.0:37:31.12.Default..0.0.0..the guards leave their posts\Nand take their positions on the Wall.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:31.29.0:37:33.84.Default..0.0.0..That is our moment.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:34.62.0:37:38.68.Default..0.0.0..We want to be riding away\Nas the battle rages.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:40.84.0:37:43.89.Default..0.0.0..And the armory doors? You have keys?
Dialogue: 0.0:37:44.01.0:37:45.81.Default..0.0.0..I have black powder.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:45.88.0:37:47.85.Default..0.0.0..Enough for several doors.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:48.43.0:37:49.85.Default..0.0.0..He brings us in. We get us out.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:55.39.0:37:58.86.Default..0.0.0..As you fought. where was this stone?
Dialogue: 0.0:37:59.40.0:38:01.37.Default..0.0.0..In my bag.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:03.36.0:38:05.24.Default..0.0.0..Its unseen force is powerful.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:05.78.0:38:08.70.Default..0.0.0..I believe this strange stone could help us.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:10.53.0:38:12.50.Default..0.0.0..We try everything.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:13.62.0:38:15.87.Default..0.0.0..Where are the Tao Tei now?
Dialogue: 0.0:38:16.00.0:38:18.42.Default..0.0.0..The mountains. regrouping.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:19.54.0:38:21.67.Default..0.0.0..Where do they come from?
Dialogue: 0.0:38:22.21.0:38:24.39.Default..0.0.0..About 20 centuries ago.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:24.92.0:38:29.30.Default..0.0.0..there was an emperor whose greed\Nbrought deep suffering to all of China.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:29.43.0:38:32.68.Default..0.0.0..The heavens sent the meteor\Nthat struck Gouwu Mountain.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:32.85.0:38:36.10.Default..0.0.0..turning it green and releasing the Tao Tei.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:36.27.0:38:40.19.Default..0.0.0..From that day on.\Nthe Tao Tei rise every 60 years
Dialogue: 0.0:38:40.36.0:38:43.11.Default..0.0.0..to scourge the north of China.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:43.27.0:38:48.91.Default..0.0.0..They come to remind us of what happens\Nwhen greed is unchecked.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:49.07.0:38:52.58.Default..0.0.0..They eat anything. alive or dead.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:52.74.0:38:54.87.Default..0.0.0..and take food to their queen.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:55.04.0:38:58.26.Default..0.0.0..She depends on her soldiers to feed her.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:58.41.0:39:03.14.Default..0.0.0..Only with the food they provide\Nis she able to multiply.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:05.21.0:39:10.47.Default..0.0.0..The capital. and its two million people.\Nis only 800 li away.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:11.39.0:39:14.31.Default..0.0.0..If the Tao Tei ever had\Nthat much nourishment.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:14.47.0:39:17.77.Default..0.0.0..no corner of the world would be safe.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:18.43.0:39:19.78.Default..0.0.0..You can't hunt them?
Dialogue: 0.0:39:19.89.0:39:21.15.Default..0.0.0..Men try.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:21.60.0:39:22.65.Default..0.0.0..They disappear.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:23.27.0:39:25.53.Default..0.0.0..We never find their bones.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:14.52.0:44:16.15.Default..0.0.0..This is envoy Shen from the palace.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:16.27.0:44:19.82.Default..0.0.0..He has brought important records\Nto help with the coming battle.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:23.99.0:44:26.41.Default..0.0.0..A 900-year-old battle report.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:26.91.0:44:29.50.Default..0.0.0..At the Hansha gates.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:29.62.0:44:32.67.Default..0.0.0..three beasts mounted the Wall.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:32.87.0:44:36.60.Default..0.0.0..They killed many men as they went forward.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:36.75.0:44:40.35.Default..0.0.0..Then. by the grace of the ancient gods.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:40.51.0:44:42.76.Default..0.0.0..the beasts stopped...
Dialogue: 0.0:44:45.68.0:44:48.93.Default..0.0.0.....and sat peacefully as we slaughtered them.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:52.23.0:44:56.61.Default..0.0.0..At the Hansha Gate.\Nwas a magnet just like this one.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:56.69.0:45:01.41.Default..0.0.0..I believe that magnet was the reason\Nthat two of you Westerners
Dialogue: 0.0:45:01.49.0:45:03.58.Default..0.0.0..killed the Tao Tei so easily.
Dialogue: 0.0:45:04.45.0:45:08.00.Default..0.0.0..I believe the magnet makes the Tao Tei deaf.
Dialogue: 0.0:45:08.62.0:45:11.54.Default..0.0.0..Without instruction. they fall still.
Dialogue: 0.0:45:15.92.0:45:17.04.Default..0.0.0..How can we be sure?
Dialogue: 0.0:45:18.79.0:45:19.89.Default..0.0.0..Why not try it?
Dialogue: 0.0:45:21.42.0:45:22.64.Default..0.0.0..Capture a Tao Tei.
Dialogue: 0.0:45:22.80.0:45:23.97.Default..0.0.0..See if it works.
Dialogue: 0.0:45:26.64.0:45:27.64.Default..0.0.0..How?
Dialogue: 0.0:45:27.76.0:45:29.76.Default..0.0.0..No net is strong enough.
Dialogue: 0.0:45:29.89.0:45:32.06.Default..0.0.0..Hunt them. Like a whale.
Dialogue: 0.0:45:32.64.0:45:34.24.Default..0.0.0..You know what that is.
Dialogue: 0.0:45:34.31.0:45:35.36.Default..0.0.0..Uh... A water beast.
Dialogue: 0.0:45:35.98.0:45:39.15.Default..0.0.0..Hundred times the size of a Tao Tei.
Dialogue: 0.0:45:39.23.0:45:43.33.Default..0.0.0..A spear that grabs.\NHook the bone. Pull them up.
Dialogue: 0.0:45:47.91.0:45:49.71.Default..0.0.0..I've seen it done in Spain.
Dialogue: 0.0:45:54.62.0:45:56.67.Default..0.0.0..What the hell are you doing?
Dialogue: 0.0:45:56.83.0:45:58.38.Default..0.0.0..We need to be free when the attack comes.
Dialogue: 0.0:45:58.46.0:45:59.88.Default..0.0.0..How many chances do you think we will get?
Dialogue: 0.0:46:02.76.0:46:06.26.Default..0.0.0..Be injured. Be missing. Be a coward.
Dialogue: 0.0:46:06.34.0:46:07.97.Default..0.0.0..Get out of this.
Dialogue: 0.0:46:09.22.0:46:10.52.Default..0.0.0..We did enough.
Dialogue: 0.0:48:03.96.0:48:04.96.Default..0.0.0..He'll be here.
Dialogue: 0.0:48:05.04.0:48:07.22.Default..0.0.0..When? When it's over?
Dialogue: 0.0:48:07.30.0:48:09.05.Default..0.0.0..We start and he will find us.
Dialogue: 0.0:48:09.13.0:48:10.18.Default..0.0.0..Start?
Dialogue: 0.0:48:10.30.0:48:11.97.Default..0.0.0..We're jumping off a cliff here.
Dialogue: 0.0:48:12.64.0:48:15.98.Default..0.0.0..I have everything. Powder. tools. maps.
Dialogue: 0.0:48:16.10.0:48:18.15.Default..0.0.0..It's all hidden and arranged along the route.
Dialogue: 0.0:48:18.31.0:48:22.19.Default..0.0.0..Once we start. there's no going back.
Dialogue: 0.0:50:06.54.0:50:08.38.Default..0.0.0..I'll find him.\N- Forget him.
Dialogue: 0.0:50:08.54.0:50:11.26.Default..0.0.0..He'd rather die trying to impress\Nthe new general
Dialogue: 0.0:50:11.38.0:50:16.05.Default..0.0.0..than grab the key to every counting\Nroom and brothel in the world.
Dialogue: 0.0:50:16.72.0:50:18.77.Default..0.0.0..Good God. man. The time is now!
Dialogue: 0.0:50:18.84.0:50:20.56.Default..0.0.0..I can't go without him.
Dialogue: 0.0:50:20.68.0:50:22.06.Default..0.0.0..More the spoils for us!
Dialogue: 0.0:50:22.14.0:50:24.14.Default..0.0.0..We need his bow!
Dialogue: 0.0:51:47.81.0:51:50.06.Default..0.0.0..No. no. no. Stop!
Dialogue: 0.0:51:50.19.0:51:51.44.Default..0.0.0..There's too much tension.
Dialogue: 0.0:51:51.52.0:51:52.99.Default..0.0.0..Chain will break.
Dialogue: 0.0:51:53.06.0:51:54.66.Default..0.0.0..That way. That way.
Dialogue: 0.0:51:54.73.0:51:55.98.Default..0.0.0..- Let him run!
Dialogue: 0.0:51:59.90.0:52:01.41.Default..0.0.0..Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0.0:52:01.53.0:52:03.87.Default..0.0.0..We need longer\Nfor the sleeping potion to work.
Dialogue: 0.0:52:08.54.0:52:09.54.Default..0.0.0..That way. That way.
Dialogue: 0.0:52:11.08.0:52:14.09.Default..0.0.0..We need to isolate it.\NSeparate it from the others.
Dialogue: 0.0:52:31.73.0:52:34.82.Default..0.0.0..The chain won't hold much longer!
Dialogue: 0.0:52:45.16.0:52:46.20.Default..0.0.0..William. wait.
Dialogue: 0.0:52:49.91.0:52:53.13.Default..0.0.0..These arrows will scream as the Tao Tei run.
Dialogue: 0.0:52:54.71.0:52:55.76.Default..0.0.0..Aim for the sound.
Dialogue: 0.0:54:20.67.0:54:23.42.Default..0.0.0..I'm only saving you so I can kill you myself.
Dialogue: 0.0:54:25.88.0:54:27.23.Default..0.0.0..Grab an ax. we're fighting blind.
Dialogue: 0.0:54:36.81.0:54:38.86.Default..0.0.0..Not yet.\N- I know what to do!
Dialogue: 0.0:55:09.18.0:55:10.18.Default..0.0.0..The fire's not holding them back.
Dialogue: 0.0:55:11.05.0:55:12.40.Default..0.0.0..Die well. brother.
Dialogue: 0.0:55:19.48.0:55:20.65.Default..0.0.0..What the hell are you doing?
Dialogue: 0.0:55:20.73.0:55:21.90.Default..0.0.0..She's listening.
Dialogue: 0.0:57:03.33.0:57:04.50.Default..0.0.0..Did it work?
Dialogue: 0.0:57:04.58.0:57:07.18.Default..0.0.0..Yes. The beast was captured.
Dialogue: 0.0:57:08.59.0:57:10.21.Default..0.0.0..My friend...
Dialogue: 0.0:57:10.51.0:57:12.18.Default..0.0.0..He was unharmed.
Dialogue: 0.0:57:22.68.0:57:25.19.Default..0.0.0..Why did you go over the Wall?
Dialogue: 0.0:57:33.28.0:57:34.87.Default..0.0.0..Did I say it right?
Dialogue: 0.0:57:38.95.0:57:40.20.Default..0.0.0..Thank you.
Dialogue: 0.0:57:46.88.0:57:48.47.Default..0.0.0..Black powder.
Dialogue: 0.0:57:50.13.0:57:52.22.Default..0.0.0..It is a terrible weapon.
Dialogue: 0.0:57:53.42.0:57:56.89.Default..0.0.0..It would be better if you had never seen it.
Dialogue: 0.0:58:01.39.0:58:04.36.Default..0.0.0..I know very little of the outside world.
Dialogue: 0.0:58:05.14.0:58:06.52.Default..0.0.0..But it seems to me.
Dialogue: 0.0:58:06.60.0:58:10.07.Default..0.0.0..the greed of men is not that different\Nfrom the Tao Tei.
Dialogue: 0.0:58:11.07.0:58:12.57.Default..0.0.0..Is that true?
Dialogue: 0.0:58:13.90.0:58:16.53.Default..0.0.0..The strong take what they want.
Dialogue: 0.0:58:27.50.0:58:29.92.Default..0.0.0..Forget what you have seen.
Dialogue: 0.0:59:52.38.0:59:53.42.Default..0.0.0..Hmm?
Dialogue: 0.0:59:54.46.0:59:56.34.Default..0.0.0..You're much braver than they think.
Dialogue: 0.1:00:25.03.1:00:26.63.Default..0.0.0..You wounded?
Dialogue: 0.1:00:29.45.1:00:31.05.Default..0.0.0..I was looking for you.
Dialogue: 0.1:00:31.96.1:00:33.13.Default..0.0.0..To say thank you.
Dialogue: 0.1:00:39.21.1:00:40.72.Default..0.0.0..You feel good. huh?
Dialogue: 0.1:00:41.97.1:00:44.14.Default..0.0.0..Maybe you sing a little song. eh?
Dialogue: 0.1:00:45.26.1:00:46.94.Default..0.0.0..I will join you.
Dialogue: 0.1:00:47.43.1:00:50.23.Default..0.0.0..We can sing together\Nhow you saved the grateful chinos.
Dialogue: 0.1:00:50.35.1:00:52.77.Default..0.0.0..You saw what happened\Nout there and that's what you say?
Dialogue: 0.1:00:52.89.1:00:53.99.Default..0.0.0..I see black powder.
Dialogue: 0.1:00:55.81.1:00:57.07.Default..0.0.0..I see a man forget his friends.
Dialogue: 0.1:00:57.73.1:00:59.70.Default..0.0.0..The black powder's not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0.1:00:59.78.1:01:01.87.Default..0.0.0..What goes nowhere is you.
Dialogue: 0.1:01:05.66.1:01:07.96.Default..0.0.0..You'll never get what you want from this.
Dialogue: 0.1:01:08.95.1:01:11.42.Default..0.0.0..You think they see you as some kind of hero?
Dialogue: 0.1:01:11.75.1:01:13.59.Default..0.0.0..A man of virtue?
Dialogue: 0.1:01:14.37.1:01:18.59.Default..0.0.0..Maybe you can fool them.\Nbut I know what you are.
Dialogue: 0.1:01:19.59.1:01:22.26.Default..0.0.0..You know what you are.
Dialogue: 0.1:01:23.18.1:01:24.64.Default..0.0.0..A thief.
Dialogue: 0.1:01:25.22.1:01:26.56.Default..0.0.0..a liar.
Dialogue: 0.1:01:28.85.1:01:30.27.Default..0.0.0..and a killer.
Dialogue: 0.1:01:32.68.1:01:37.06.Default..0.0.0..And you can never undo the things you\Nhave done. and you will never be anything.
Dialogue: 0.1:01:45.82.1:01:47.45.Default..0.0.0..Good to see you again. amigo.
Dialogue: 0.1:02:08.64.1:02:10.44.Default..0.0.0..Nothing?\N- No.
Dialogue: 0.1:02:10.51.1:02:11.77.Default..0.0.0..How do you know he won't betray us?
Dialogue: 0.1:02:11.85.1:02:12.97.Default..0.0.0..I don't.
Dialogue: 0.1:02:13.06.1:02:14.81.Default..0.0.0..They'll kill him.\NThey'll kill him no matter what.
Dialogue: 0.1:02:14.89.1:02:16.86.Default..0.0.0..The time they spend killing him
Dialogue: 0.1:02:17.98.1:02:20.15.Default..0.0.0..is time they are not chasing us.
Dialogue: 0.1:03:02.32.1:03:05.36.Default..0.0.0..Careful with that. There's powder here.
Dialogue: 0.1:03:17.54.1:03:19.04.Default..0.0.0..Tovar.
Dialogue: 0.1:04:18.39.1:04:21.11.Default..0.0.0..Have a look. See if it's gone out.
Dialogue: 0.1:04:21.48.1:04:22.60.Default..0.0.0..Is it safe?
Dialogue: 0.1:04:22.77.1:04:24.27.Default..0.0.0..Of course it is.
Dialogue: 0.1:04:53.13.1:04:55.51.Default..0.0.0..Shake it off. man. To work.
Dialogue: 0.1:04:58.85.1:05:01.19.Default..0.0.0..I thought you said it was safe?
Dialogue: 0.1:05:02.10.1:05:03.70.Default..0.0.0..We're in. aren't we?
Dialogue: 0.1:05:15.53.1:05:16.91.Default..0.0.0..You're here.
Dialogue: 0.1:05:17.49.1:05:19.04.Default..0.0.0..We've come to our senses. eh?
Dialogue: 0.1:05:19.70.1:05:20.95.Default..0.0.0..Ballard has planned well.
Dialogue: 0.1:05:21.04.1:05:22.91.Default..0.0.0..Getting out is easy.
Dialogue: 0.1:05:23.00.1:05:25.34.Default..0.0.0..There's a gate. 20 miles west.
Dialogue: 0.1:05:25.50.1:05:27.34.Default..0.0.0..We dodge the hill tribes.
Dialogue: 0.1:05:28.50.1:05:29.50.Default..0.0.0..We can make it.
Dialogue: 0.1:05:30.88.1:05:32.01.Default..0.0.0..They need us here.
Dialogue: 0.1:05:32.09.1:05:33.89.Default..0.0.0..They need more than us.
Dialogue: 0.1:05:34.84.1:05:36.19.Default..0.0.0..These people are doomed.
Dialogue: 0.1:05:36.30.1:05:37.35.Default..0.0.0..Don't be a fool.
Dialogue: 0.1:05:37.47.1:05:38.44.Default..0.0.0..I've been a fool.
Dialogue: 0.1:05:38.51.1:05:40.27.Default..0.0.0..I'm done with it.
Dialogue: 0.1:05:40.85.1:05:42.19.Default..0.0.0..Brother. please.
Dialogue: 0.1:05:43.35.1:05:45.35.Default..0.0.0..We've been fighting for nothing.
Dialogue: 0.1:05:46.19.1:05:47.48.Default..0.0.0..For greed.
Dialogue: 0.1:05:48.02.1:05:51.24.Default..0.0.0..Amigo. after all the blood.
Dialogue: 0.1:05:51.32.1:05:53.82.Default..0.0.0..and cold. and pain.
Dialogue: 0.1:05:53.95.1:05:56.32.Default..0.0.0..with this black powder in our saddle bags.
Dialogue: 0.1:05:56.41.1:05:57.91.Default..0.0.0..we win.
Dialogue: 0.1:05:59.20.1:06:00.42.Default..0.0.0..You come with me.
Dialogue: 0.1:06:02.20.1:06:03.46.Default..0.0.0..I can't do that now.
Dialogue: 0.1:06:05.67.1:06:06.71.Default..0.0.0..Stay and fight.
Dialogue: 0.1:06:08.13.1:06:09.38.Default..0.0.0..William...
Dialogue: 0.1:06:13.92.1:06:15.02.Default..0.0.0..Think he's dead?
Dialogue: 0.1:06:15.09.1:06:17.14.Default..0.0.0..It'd take a lot more than that.
Dialogue: 0.1:07:09.19.1:07:10.44.Default..0.0.0..Come on.
Dialogue: 0.1:07:10.94.1:07:11.99.Default..0.0.0..Hyah.
Dialogue: 0.1:08:35.36.1:08:38.20.Default..0.0.0..I tried to stop them...\N- You dare to speak to me?
Dialogue: 0.1:08:40.19.1:08:41.45.Default..0.0.0..I didn't do this.
Dialogue: 0.1:08:42.03.1:08:45.03.Default..0.0.0..And you came here to trade.
Dialogue: 0.1:08:45.20.1:08:47.04.Default..0.0.0..And you knew nothing of black powder.
Dialogue: 0.1:08:49.20.1:08:51.67.Default..0.0.0..What a fool you must think I am.
Dialogue: 0.1:08:51.75.1:08:54.00.Default..0.0.0..If I was with them. why would I be here?
Dialogue: 0.1:08:54.08.1:08:55.18.Default..0.0.0..I tried to stop them. I tried...
Dialogue: 0.1:08:57.88.1:08:59.26.Default..0.0.0..You lie.
Dialogue: 0.1:09:00.92.1:09:03.02.Default..0.0.0..Some part of you knows that's not true.
Dialogue: 0.1:09:03.09.1:09:08.02.Default..0.0.0..If I were not the General.\NI would kill you myself.
Dialogue: 0.1:10:27.22.1:10:28.97.Default..0.0.0..Which way. left or right?
Dialogue: 0.1:10:29.64.1:10:32.44.Default..0.0.0..Go up and take a look from the high ground.
Dialogue: 0.1:10:44.49.1:10:45.99.Default..0.0.0..- Hyah!
Dialogue: 0.1:10:47.32.1:10:48.41.Default..0.0.0..No!
Dialogue: 0.1:10:48.99.1:10:51.49.Default..0.0.0..No! Bastard!
Dialogue: 0.1:12:12.78.1:12:14.16.Default..0.0.0..What happened?
Dialogue: 0.1:12:17.20.1:12:18.38.Default..0.0.0..What happened?
Dialogue: 0.1:12:18.50.1:12:20.34.Default..0.0.0..We have failed.
Dialogue: 0.1:12:20.50.1:12:22.92.Default..0.0.0..The Tao Tei are in the Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0.1:12:23.50.1:12:26.93.Default..0.0.0..You are free to leave.\NTake what you wish and go.
Dialogue: 0.1:12:27.05.1:12:29.09.Default..0.0.0..This was the General's final order.
Dialogue: 0.1:12:29.22.1:12:30.39.Default..0.0.0..Where is she?
Dialogue: 0.1:12:34.97.1:12:36.39.Default..0.0.0..To do what?
Dialogue: 0.1:12:36.47.1:12:37.60.Default..0.0.0..To fight?
Dialogue: 0.1:12:37.72.1:12:39.02.Default..0.0.0..Is there a chance?
Dialogue: 0.1:12:39.14.1:12:40.27.Default..0.0.0..There's only one.
Dialogue: 0.1:12:40.77.1:12:42.77.Default..0.0.0..Kill the Queen.
Dialogue: 0.1:12:42.85.1:12:45.03.Default..0.0.0..Kill the Queen. or we all die.
Dialogue: 0.1:12:46.86.1:12:47.95.Default..0.0.0..Leave.
Dialogue: 0.1:12:48.53.1:12:52.87.Default..0.0.0..Tell the world what you have seen.\Nand tell them what is coming.
Dialogue: 0.1:13:15.89.1:13:17.51.Default..0.0.0..I'll need my bow.
Dialogue: 0.1:13:21.27.1:13:23.82.Default..0.0.0..If I'm to join you. I'll need my bow.
Dialogue: 0.1:13:35.36.1:13:37.41.Default..0.0.0..He wishes to join us.
Dialogue: 0.1:15:31.90.1:15:32.94.Default..0.0.0..No.
Dialogue: 0.1:15:33.02.1:15:34.03.Default..0.0.0..No.
Dialogue: 0.1:15:38.70.1:15:39.70.Default..0.0.0..No.
Dialogue: 0.1:15:44.58.1:15:45.58.Default..0.0.0..No.
Dialogue: 0.1:15:47.12.1:15:50.13.Default..0.0.0..No. don't throw that thing near fire!
Dialogue: 0.1:17:09.37.1:17:10.75.Default..0.0.0..Above you!
Dialogue: 0.1:17:24.97.1:17:26.56.Default..0.0.0..Behind you!
Dialogue: 0.1:17:39.15.1:17:40.74.Default..0.0.0..I set you free.
Dialogue: 0.1:17:41.74.1:17:43.08.Default..0.0.0..And here I am.
Dialogue: 0.1:17:44.78.1:17:45.91.Default..0.0.0..There's the Queen!
Dialogue: 0.1:17:50.87.1:17:53.29.Default..0.0.0..They will not attack\Nwhile the Queen is feeding.
Dialogue: 0.1:17:53.41.1:17:55.34.Default..0.0.0..We have a chance!
Dialogue: 0.1:17:55.42.1:17:56.51.Default..0.0.0..Hold on!
Dialogue: 0.1:19:18.50.1:19:20.34.Default..0.0.0..There is an underground canal here.
Dialogue: 0.1:19:20.50.1:19:22.34.Default..0.0.0..Has it been breached?
Dialogue: 0.1:19:22.42.1:19:23.92.Default..0.0.0..The Tao Tei should all be above ground.
Dialogue: 0.1:19:24.63.1:19:25.85.Default..0.0.0..And the one we captured?
Dialogue: 0.1:19:26.34.1:19:27.34.Default..0.0.0..We load it up.
Dialogue: 0.1:19:28.47.1:19:29.81.Default..0.0.0..We feed it.
Dialogue: 0.1:19:29.89.1:19:31.85.Default..0.0.0..And it will return to its Queen.
Dialogue: 0.1:19:32.05.1:19:33.02.Default..0.0.0..Good.
Dialogue: 0.1:20:42.25.1:20:44.55.Default..0.0.0..You'll have one hell of a scar.\Nbut you'll live.
Dialogue: 0.1:20:47.71.1:20:49.39.Default..0.0.0..We'll come back for him.
Dialogue: 0.1:21:07.40.1:21:08.87.Default..0.0.0..They've broken through!
Dialogue: 0.1:22:31.36.1:22:33.99.Default..0.0.0..Patience. William.
Dialogue: 0.1:22:50.96.1:22:54.06.Default..0.0.0..And it will go to the Queen when it's done?
Dialogue: 0.1:22:54.30.1:22:55.52.Default..0.0.0..It should.
Dialogue: 0.1:22:58.05.1:22:59.10.Default..0.0.0..It will.
Dialogue: 0.1:23:11.06.1:23:12.07.Default..0.0.0..Let it in.
Dialogue: 0.1:23:36.13.1:23:37.43.Default..0.0.0..I can get a shot from above.
Dialogue: 0.1:23:42.47.1:23:44.77.Default..0.0.0..Go! I'll hold them back.
Dialogue: 0.1:24:07.79.1:24:09.29.Default..0.0.0..Wait. Not yet.
Dialogue: 0.1:24:17.88.1:24:18.97.Default..0.0.0..Hit.
Dialogue: 0.1:24:28.14.1:24:29.11.Default..0.0.0..Go higher.
Dialogue: 0.1:24:29.18.1:24:30.65.Default..0.0.0..I'll get a better shot.
Dialogue: 0.1:24:43.95.1:24:44.95.Default..0.0.0..General!
Dialogue: 0.1:24:45.03.1:24:46.33.Default..0.0.0..It's up to you now!
Dialogue: 0.1:25:39.21.1:25:40.84.Default..0.0.0..We have one black powder weapon left.
Dialogue: 0.1:25:40.92.1:25:42.39.Default..0.0.0..Give me the spear.
Dialogue: 0.1:25:44.55.1:25:46.02.Default..0.0.0..I've trained for this my whole life.
Dialogue: 0.1:25:53.06.1:25:54.19.Default..0.0.0..I'll get you the shot.
Dialogue: 0.1:26:40.32.1:26:41.61.Default..0.0.0..I've got you.
Dialogue: 0.1:27:59.52.1:28:01.61.Default..0.0.0..So. how's life without me?
Dialogue: 0.1:28:02.86.1:28:04.28.Default..0.0.0..A little slow.
Dialogue: 0.1:28:07.53.1:28:09.15.Default..0.0.0..You're a hero after all.
Dialogue: 0.1:28:09.70.1:28:10.95.Default..0.0.0..Well. it looks that way.
Dialogue: 0.1:28:11.03.1:28:13.38.Default..0.0.0..You seem pleased with yourself.
Dialogue: 0.1:28:13.45.1:28:15.87.Default..0.0.0..And what are they giving you\Nfor all of your troubles?
Dialogue: 0.1:28:16.04.1:28:17.04.Default..0.0.0..A bag of gold?
Dialogue: 0.1:28:17.62.1:28:19.79.Default..0.0.0..A victory parade along the top of the Wall?
Dialogue: 0.1:28:20.37.1:28:22.30.Default..0.0.0..All the black powder I can carry.
Dialogue: 0.1:28:22.88.1:28:25.60.Default..0.0.0..And a cavalry escort to get me home safely.
Dialogue: 0.1:28:26.71.1:28:28.06.Default..0.0.0..Well. congratulations.
Dialogue: 0.1:28:28.13.1:28:29.97.Default..0.0.0..Thank you.
Dialogue: 0.1:28:30.05.1:28:33.35.Default..0.0.0..So what is this?\NYou're here to rub my nose in it?
Dialogue: 0.1:28:33.55.1:28:34.98.Default..0.0.0..Well. would you blame me?
Dialogue: 0.1:28:35.06.1:28:37.43.Default..0.0.0..The last time I saw you.\Nyou left me for dead.
Dialogue: 0.1:28:37.56.1:28:39.48.Default..0.0.0..And the time before that. I saved your life.
Dialogue: 0.1:28:39.56.1:28:40.90.Default..0.0.0..True.
Dialogue: 0.1:28:43.23.1:28:45.82.Default..0.0.0..You know. the Emperor gave me a choice.
Dialogue: 0.1:28:45.90.1:28:48.12.Default..0.0.0..I could take the black powder.
Dialogue: 0.1:28:48.28.1:28:50.62.Default..0.0.0..or I could take you.
Dialogue: 0.1:28:52.45.1:28:54.42.Default..0.0.0..Please tell me you chose the powder?
Dialogue: 0.1:29:01.67.1:29:03.38.Default..0.0.0..I don't even know you anymore.
Dialogue: 0.1:29:06.09.1:29:07.71.Default..0.0.0..The horses are saddled and waiting.
Dialogue: 0.1:29:07.80.1:29:10.09.Default..0.0.0..Best we ride before nightfall.
Dialogue: 0.1:29:15.60.1:29:17.27.Default..0.0.0..I'll be inside.
Dialogue: 0.1:29:17.35.1:29:19.22.Default..0.0.0..Don't leave without me.
Dialogue: 0.1:29:29.94.1:29:31.12.Default..0.0.0..I came to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0.1:29:33.45.1:29:36.70.Default..0.0.0..I understand congratulations are in order.
Dialogue: 0.1:29:36.87.1:29:39.12.Default..0.0.0..General of the northwest territory.
Dialogue: 0.1:29:39.29.1:29:40.96.Default..0.0.0..That's quite an honor.
Dialogue: 0.1:29:43.46.1:29:45.58.Default..0.0.0..Seems you've made your choice.
Dialogue: 0.1:29:45.71.1:29:46.80.Default..0.0.0..Him?
Dialogue: 0.1:29:46.96.1:29:49.84.Default..0.0.0..Believe me. I'm already thinking about\Ntrading him back for the powder.
Dialogue: 0.1:29:50.01.1:29:51.97.Default..0.0.0..I heard that.
Dialogue: 0.1:29:57.64.1:30:00.77.Default..0.0.0..Perhaps we were both wrong.
Dialogue: 0.1:30:01.31.1:30:03.98.Default..0.0.0..We are more similar than I thought.
Dialogue: 0.1:30:09.65.1:30:11.37.Default..0.0.0..Thank you. General.
Dialogue: 0.1:30:37.30.1:30:39.35.Default..0.0.0..Are you sure you don't want to go back?
Dialogue: 0.1:30:40.01.1:30:41.01.Default..0.0.0..Of course I do.
Dialogue: 0.1:30:42.18.1:30:44.69.Default..0.0.0..I just don't trust you\Nto make it out of here alone.
